dct_title_s: La Palestina, Giudea, Terra Promessa o Terra Sancta
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Bar scale on map given in "Leghe di Francia".
Shows topography, drainage, territories of the twelve tribes of Israel, places of historical interest.
